<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和鲍比向地面坠落的速度更快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们抓住了彼此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比！”赛伊大叫着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拍打你的翅膀。一直拍打它们不要停！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这对兄弟很快重新掌握了飞翔的技巧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们向上朝着姐妹们飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚刚实在太惊险了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊颤抖着声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟朝周围看了一圈儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她发现了一根粗壮的树枝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去那里休息一会吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们朝着那棵树飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简突然问道：“我们要怎么降落？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须像收伞那样把翅膀收起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65695</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿潘瑟回答说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65696</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来试试看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟朝着那棵树飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的一只翅膀收了起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但另一只却挂在了树叶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”她大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的孩子就跟在她后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊平稳地落在了树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比也没有什么问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们做到了！”男孩子们喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们咧开嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但简却并不想休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有很多时间了。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想尽可能地多飞一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她昂起头，飞得更高了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们最好待在一起。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以其他人也跟着简飞了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们飞过了湖泊和高山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们飞过去的时候，鸟儿大声地发出了抗议。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了好一会，鲍比说：“我饿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我们能去哪里弄点吃的呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟大声地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能带着这些东西到处走啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊指着自己的翅膀说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要把他们的翅膀藏起来是不可能做到的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们高高低低地飞着去寻找食物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们什么都没找到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道我们去哪里可以找到吃的。”赛伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“农夫詹金斯自己做果酱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫詹金斯是玛莎阿姨的邻居。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有时候他会给玛莎阿姨送自己家做的面包和果酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说从他那里偷吃的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是偷。我们只是借。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个主意太糟糕了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟指责说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你有更好的主意吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊反击说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟当然什么主意都没想出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧！如果你保证，我们会把拿的东西再还回去的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她最终同意了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，那就跟我来吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊转身飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们飞到农场的时候，已经接近傍晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他可能将食物放在谷仓里了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谷仓有两层。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幸运的是，第二层有扇很大的窗户是开着的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们从那扇窗飞了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊发现了几个木箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们装满了果酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们一句话都没说就开始吃果酱了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这真好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260700</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比舔着嘴唇说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须记清楚我们吃了多少。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 潘瑟边说边数空果酱罐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！太阳开始落山了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简指着闪耀着红色光芒的天空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们突然感觉自己变轻了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就好像他们的肩膀上少了些重量似的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“翅膀不见了。”简轻声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在自己平滑的后背上四处摸着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，我们现在必须从这里出去了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但没有翅膀，孩子们就不能再飞出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大门在一楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里都是动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以从这个梯子上爬下去。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一层的中间，有一个大大的正方形开口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>开口里放着一架梯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊爬到了梯子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来吧！”赛伊边说边往下爬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个孩子都到了一楼后，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>动物们开始变得吵嚷起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘！”潘瑟对着一头叫得特别欢的马小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>89</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊朝着谷仓大门走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>90</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>351891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拉了拉门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>91</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门一点儿都没开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>92</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又试了一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>93</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>364817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，赛伊睁大了双眼看着他的兄弟姐妹们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>94</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>364818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>368251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“门锁上了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>